Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:18.28,Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\fs16\alpha&H66&\an7\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H0075EA&}ACG12调查小队【沉默似金_】抄自【F宅字幕组】\N仅供学习交流，禁止用于任何商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.01,0:00:04.68,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,小哥 别傻站在那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:05.53,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,菲鲁特？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.53,0:00:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然是同年级的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:09.57,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,哈？这不是当然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:12.14,Default - italics,Subaru,0,0,0,,居然和这种小孩子是同级生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.14,0:00:14.14,Default - italics,Subaru,0,0,0,,真是可怕的异世界现实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:18.28,Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\an2}{\c&H6E3C42&}Re:{\c&H6E48B4&}小{\c&H317FB6&}剧场{\c&H060200&}之二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:22.70,SignC,Title,0,0,0,,{\fs26}{\1c&H9D81FF&}小{\1c&H59B9FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}剧场{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HC4C700&\b1\bord6}②{\bord2}{\1c&H775DFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}自{\1c&HD097A8&\3c&HFFFFFF&}称{\1c&HCFD000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}老师{\1c&H9D81FF&}、{\1c&H59B9FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}碧{\1c&HD097A8&\3c&HFFFFFF&}翠{\1c&HCFD000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}丝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:20.62,Default - Top,Beatrice,0,0,0,,那边的那两个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:23.39,Default - Top,Beatrice,0,0,0,,你们吵吵闹闹的打扰到上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:24.99,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,快点回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:26.96,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,你看 这就来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:28.15,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,呃 谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:29.41,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,哪位男性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,快闭上你的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.79,0:00:33.19,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,喂喂碧翠子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这里在设定上可是学校哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:37.28,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,不是小孩子该来的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:40.15,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.15,0:00:42.64,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,喂 小哥 你还是快点道歉会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.15,0:00:43.21,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,{\an8}你先是跟我说话 然后还把我抱了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:43.97,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你知道你的行为是多么可怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我做的事就和平时做的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:49.21,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,对老师要放尊重一些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:51.55,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,等等 碧翠子你刚刚说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:54.15,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,我说你一点都不懂礼仪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:56.78,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,不是这个 你刚刚说自己是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:01.59,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,怎么了 你对碧翠丝老师我有什么想说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.59,0:01:03.29,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,比起有什么想说的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,完全是有一大堆想说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:06.89,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,非要只说一个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:08.41,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,你怎么看都是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:10.25,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,这种事想想就算了 不能说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.18,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,退一百步 菲鲁特是同级生也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.18,0:01:15.60,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,碧翠子居然是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.27,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,呜哇 我说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.27,0:01:17.81,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:21.11,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,和老师吵架会遭遇什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就让我来告诉你吧嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:25.51,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,糟糕 老师我可没做错事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:27.00,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,这手势是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:29.94,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我只会惩罚这位男性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:33.42,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,真心住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:35.07,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,小哥 要坚强地活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:36.15,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,菲鲁特你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:37.67,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,等等 有话好说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:39.58,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,事到如今 已不会再原谅你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:42.42,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,住手住手不要再吸走魔力了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.36,0:01:49.55,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,出 出现了 碧翠丝老师的必杀挠痒痒攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:53.15,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,哼 长记性了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:54.76,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,居然是挠痒痒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:57.65,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,我还以为又会被吸走魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:00.28,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,魔 魔力 你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:02.58,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,诶 就是魔力啊魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:05.27,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,我还以为一定会被你吸干魔力来着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:08.00,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,把魔力吸干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.12,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,这可真是粗俗的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:12.13,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,贝蒂是绝对不会做那种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:14.79,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,是啊小哥 那种事是绝不可能发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:15.46,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:18.36,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,我虽然明白你想这那么做的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,无论怎么说魔力都应该是佐料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:20.65,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,唔?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:24.70,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,一提到魔力就很想吃了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:25.52,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:28.78,Default,Beatrice,0,0,0,,特别是加载炸鸡上简直是人间美味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:30.22,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,等一下 那个大概是蛋黄酱
